{"tid":664679,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有線：【深圳掛牌或要停牌 樂視網：現金極度短缺】","createTime":"2018-05-14T09:41:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T10:16:11.000Z","uid":20815,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9b0e6af97de4e9bf67f9694bd2a6fef5d459602a","tid":664679,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T09:41:33.000Z","msg":"在深交所掛牌的樂視網說，目前現金流極度緊張，並存在被暫停上市風險。<br />\n<br />\n樂視網在業績說明會上表示，如果今個年度的審計報告連續第二年被評定『無法表示意見』，按深交所規定，存在被暫停上市風險。<br />\n<br />\n公司又指目前資金安排存在「極大困難」，現金流極度緊張，正尋求一切可能方案，但尚未形成確定方案。<br />\n<br />\n由於部份資產被凍結，目前資產融資難以覆蓋短期債務，加上公司披露的上市公司累計訴訟及仲裁情況，如果訴訟賠償進一步形成，將加重債務壓力。<br />\n<br />\n公司說，不了解創辦人賈躍亭的汽車業務進展，但時刻關注對方涉及的關聯欠款問題，期望對方盡快確認有效的解決方案及還款時間表，及時挽救樂視網。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/14/cBVOvt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F14%2FcBVOvt.png&h=5f90d9c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9853a759a40a36c81b513987a44485fdfbd69bb0","tid":664679,"uid":20815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T09:42:39.000Z","msg":"燒山一出，誰興燈風 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a7db7991275c1d12f5390b1deb7f89cefed0b5d","tid":664679,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T09:44:57.000Z","msg":"燒山好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e8384169965cbb8c2928c3f5dc5b48683eebbd","tid":664679,"uid":183429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T09:47:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.g